00:30:24,430 --> 00:30:24,690
Yes.

660
00:30:26,110 --> 00:30:27,090
Are you sure?

661
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:28,090
Yes.

662
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:30,980
I believe it's something worth pursuing.

663
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:32,620
It can be planned for

664
00:30:33,350 --> 00:30:36,460
