672
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:57,700
A natural additional experience.

673
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:00,900
So don't chase happiness directly.

674
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:02,100
What you should do

675
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:05,140
is pursue self-fulfillment.

676
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:06,570
Then happiness

677
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:08,090
will naturally follow.

678
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:13,530
